					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The high three bits of $4016 and $4017 are open bus.<br /><br />The controller data will be accessed when the strobe is high and then low, so the emulator should read them while the strobe is high, making the data available to the emulated program when it is low.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="gopher://zzo38computer.org/" class="postlink">.</a></div>
