					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">As for WHEN to poll the controllers, that's up to you. On a real NES, the controllers can be read several times per frame and the data returned will always reflect their current state. In an emulator you will most likely read the actual control(er)s once per frame and return that to the game as many times as it requests.</div>

